# Alpha
clear
units		real
dimension 3
boundary        p p p
atom_style	charge
newton on
read_data       OH_2.lmp
  orthogonal box = (0 0 0) to (16.525 16.526 16.526)
  2 by 2 by 2 MPI processor grid
  reading atoms ...
  98 atoms
